{"tid":2413316,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"寒流大停電引民怨 德州一市長稱「強者才能生存」挨轟辭職","createTime":"2021-02-18T15:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T04:54:22.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2e801f031acd1f5404b0e0a20b592a88f2438d","tid":2413316,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國德州近日遭遇史無前例的寒流侵襲，甚至引發大規模停電，民眾抱怨連連。外媒報導，轄下科羅拉多市市長鮑伊德（Tim Boyd）近日疑因發布含有「只有強者才能生存，弱者將滅亡」等內容的貼文，惹毛一票群眾後辭職下台。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，據網路流傳的貼文顯示，鮑伊德寫到，包含市郡、電力供應商等相關單位在內，「沒有人欠你或你的家人什麼」，並直呼「受夠民眾尋求支援」，若沒水沒電要想辦法自救，不要懶惰只會等待救援，「惟有強者才能生存，弱者將滅亡」（Only the strong will survive and the weak will perish）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3442398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3442398&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=436a2313\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3442398&h=e956285d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3442398</a>"},{"pid":"2e3647c43c19009816c9fd7ac8545bf2fa1c13f7","tid":2413316,"uid":233791,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"州長：Electricity is for the weak <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f735e6a84b392d0aa97a7989cdabdd72cf94aab","tid":2413316,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ddb1f958202d898c7dd5adfb3075d3579f3679","tid":2413316,"uid":116960,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:13:07.000Z","msg":"德州連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d53b598a39ab60dae8d43973017db2128d9741d","tid":2413316,"uid":289708,"like":8,"dislike